                      LORING WOLCOTT & COOLIDGE FIDUCIARY ADVISORS LLP
                    

HTTP://WWW.LWCOTRUST.COM
•   BOSTON, MA
                          • Investment Advisor
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Loring Wolcott & Coolidge Fiduciary Advisors LLP is based out of Boston. Loring Wolcott & Coolidge Fiduciary Advisors LLP is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $5,956,507,415 (Form ADV from 2016-06-01).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $4,784,713,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 35.41%. Loring Wolcott & Coolidge Fiduciary Advisors LLP's largest holding is MasterCard Inc. Class A with shares held of 2,194,085.  Loring Wolcott & Coolidge Fiduciary Advisors LLP has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 68 13F filings in our database for Loring Wolcott & Coolidge Fiduciary Advisors LLP. 
                                           






